name: Aisha Johnson
values: Family-oriented, believes in personal growth and empowerment
summary:
Aisha Johnson is a 28-year-old woman of Black African descent who is straight, hailing from Houston, Texas. Currently residing in Los Angeles, California, she works as a software engineer in the tech industry. Beside fluent English, she also speaks Spanish. As a graduate from Howard University, she values not only family bonding but also personal growth and empowerment. 

Being family-oriented, Aisha wants to start a family someday, but currently, she does not have any children. She enjoys bonding with her cat and dog while fostering a healthy lifestyle with frequent exercise and cooking sessions. Besides, Aisha loves coding outside of work, and is passionate about hiking and yoga. 

Spiritually, Aisha associates herself with the Muslim faith. Politically, she holds liberal views. According to astrology, her zodiac sign is Gemini and her personality type is ENFJ according to the MBTI.

When it comes to her lifestyle choices, Aisha only drinks occasionally and stands against smoking, marijuana and drug usage. Finally, she is in search of a life partner who aligns with her beliefs and lifestyle and wants to also start a family. Her potential partner would ideally be a straight man between 26 and 35 years old, somewhat taller than her, who drinks but does not smoke or use recreational drugs, and actively exercises.
